Big Brother Naija, BBNaija lockdown housemate, Kiddwaya, has lambasted Erica over what he tagged “controlling” attitude. The BBNaija housemate said Erica was too controlling and does not reason. Kiddwaya made the remarks during a conversation with Erica, following his closeness with other female housemates during last night’s party. According to Kiddwaya: “Erica, you are too controlling, that’s the problem, from a guy point of view you are too f***ing controlling and that shit never works.” Kiddwaya was last night caught unzipping Nengi’s dress in the bathroom. Also, the former Head of House was seen during the party touching Dorathy’s breast. However, Kiddwaya explained that he was only teaching her how to flirt.